    <reapack name="Drums MultiChannel Splitter" type="script" desc="Taal Drum Multitrack Splitter">
      <metadata>
        <description><![CDATA[
# TaalTools - Drum Multichannel Track Splitter

Professional drum track processor that automatically splits a 32-channel recording into 15 properly named and routed stereo tracks. 
Ideal for studio drum recordings with standardized input configurations.

## Features
- Automatically creates 15 stereo tracks 
- Sets up proper channel routing
- Names and colors tracks according to common drum standards
- Supports channels 3-32 for standard recording setups
]]></description>
      </metadata>
      <version name="1.0" author="Taal">
        <changelog><![CDATA[Initial Release]]></changelog>
        <source main="main" file="Scripts/TaalTools/scripts/Drums_MultiChannelSplitter.lua">https://github.com/OseMine/TaalTools/raw/main/Scripts/TaalTools/scripts/Drums_MultiChannelSplitter.lua</source>
      </version>
    </reapack>
    <reapack name="Bus Creator" type="script" desc="Bus Creator Utility">
      <metadata>
        <description><![CDATA[
# TaalTools - Bus Creator

Creates a bus track and automatically routes selected tracks to it.

## Features
- Creates a new bus track
- Routes selected tracks' channels 1/2 to the bus
- Disables master/parent send on selected tracks
]]></description>
